WEBVTT

32:47.010 --> 32:49.980 line:80%
"The ox carries spring to plow
the green fields."

32:49.980 --> 32:51.900 line:80%
It means that when spring comes
next year,

32:51.900 --> 32:53.290 line:80%
there will be a bumper harvest,

32:53.290 --> 32:55.890 line:80%
and the whole family
will be happy and healthy.
